    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone looking for a dependable daily driver rather than a perfect exterior. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the body shows signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches on the passenger side and some minor fading on the hood's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining on the rear seats, and the air conditioning remains cold and effective. It has been regularly serviced, though it will likely need new tires within the next year.",
